::Killfest/Demise/Greven/Scyther/EndBringer::

Killfest nods, activating an internal communication system between 
his team. It was virualy untracable.

"Everyone," he says into it, "Out into the hallway. The leader wants 
to see up all."

He stands up. "They're waiting in the hallway."
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
His team piles out of the door, waiting in the hallway by his room, 
expecting to see a large fearful bot as the Predacon commander.
